<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idefe372f5-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s6406"><num value="6406">§ 6406.</num><heading> Regulations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary may issue such regulations as may be necessary to carry out this chapter and the powers vested in the Secretary by this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idefe372f6-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/101/624/tXIX/s1999G">Pub. L. 101–624, title XIX, § 1999G</ref>, <date date="1990-11-28">Nov. 28, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/3916">104 Stat. 3916</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
